the background music has changed?

298
00:15:03,030 --> 00:15:03,470
Yes.

299
00:15:03,780 --> 00:15:05,030
He switched to "Wildflowers".

300
00:15:05,333 --> 00:15:07,180
No longer
listening to "Butterfly Lovers"?

301
00:15:07,820 --> 00:15:08,420
Not bad.

302
00:15:09,180 --> 00:15:09,940
Dad has cheered up.

303
00:15:11,390 --> 00:15:12,270
I told you.

304
00:15:12,700 --> 00:15:13,700
Hospitals

305
00:15:13,700 --> 00:15:15,117
are good schools.

306
00:15:15,510 --> 00:15:17,390
When a person gets hospitalized,

307
00:15:17,780 --> 00:15:19,510
many things
naturally become clear to them.

308
00:15:20,060 --> 00:15:21,510
Yeah, it's really

309
00:15:22,270 --> 00:15:23,350
a good school.

310
00:15:26,150 --> 00:15:26,750
Lina.

311
00:15:27,540 --> 00:15:29,820
Why do I feel like
you mean something else?

312
00:15:30,510 --> 00:15:31,990
Are you hiding something from me?

313
00:15:32,420 --> 00:15:33,060
No.

314
00:15:33,510 --> 00:15:34,300
Really.

315
00:15:38,110 --> 00:15:40,350
Why close the door then?

316
00:15:40,800 --> 00:15:42,288
Just say what you want to say.

317
00:15:42,820 --> 00:15:43,820
You made me say it.

318
00:15:45,030 --> 00:15:46,230
I just think

319
00:15:47,630 --> 00:15:49,540
love is really nourishing.

320
00:15:49,990 --> 00:15:51,900
Shen Dai, why don't you find a partner?

321
00:15:54,510 --> 00:15:55,030
Liu Lina.

322
00:15:55,820 --> 00:15:58,150
Do women like matchmaking

323
00:15:58,150 --> 00:15:59,700
when they get older?

324
00:16:00,180 --> 00:16:00,940
Shen Dai.

325
00:16:00,990 --> 00:16:02,133
Alright, I'll stop talking.

326
00:16:02,420 --> 00:16:03,180
I'm busy. Bye.

327
00:16:08,350 --> 00:16:09,150
Shen Qing.

328
00:16:09,750 --> 00:16:11,750
How can your sister
be so unappreciative?

329
00:16:12,420 --> 00:16:13,180
What did she do?

330
00:16:13,630 --> 00:16:15,420
I just asked her to find a partner,

331
00:16:16,030 --> 00:16:17,150
and she got angry with me.

332
00:16:17,377 --> 00:16:18,060
She even asked,

333
00:16:18,060 --> 00:16:20,350
"Do women like matchmaking
when they get older?"

334
00:16:21,230 --> 00:16:22,660
I sincerely thank your whole family.

335
00:16:22,660 --> 00:16:23,700
Calling me old?

336
00:16:24,044 --> 00:16:25,900
I got older
from doing chores for your family.

337
00:16:26,510 --> 00:16:28,300
She's been hurt in relationships before.

338
00:16:28,300 --> 00:16:29,350
You know that.

339
00:16:29,660 --> 00:16:32,110
That scumbag
had her wrapped around his finger,

340
00:16:32,110 --> 00:16:33,510
and she endured it in silence.

341
00:16:33,580 --> 00:16:35,580
No need to bring up irrelevant history.

342
00:16:36,400 --> 00:16:38,660
If I don't talk about it,
no one in your family will.

343
00:16:39,230 --> 00:16:41,230
Shen Dai is still living abroad
at an old age.

344
00:16:41,660 --> 00:16:42,820
She's all alone.

345
00:16:42,820 --> 00:16:44,533
What should she do when she gets old?

346
00:16:46,180 --> 00:16:46,580
Besides,

347
00:16:46,800 --> 00:16:48,355
when are you going to tell your sister

348
00:16:48,940 --> 00:16:50,540
about your dad and Ms. Lian?

349
00:16:51,420 --> 00:16:52,180
Don't bother.

350
00:16:52,444 --> 00:16:54,111
I'll find a chance to tell her.

351
00:17:02,577 --> 00:17:04,340
(WeChat: Shen Dai)
She's complaining about me.

352
00:17:05,430 --> 00:17:06,860
Qing, control your wife.

353
00:17:06,977 --> 00:17:08,540
Can she have some sense of boundaries?

354
00:17:08,644 --> 00:17:10,380
She keeps persuading me to get married.

355
00:17:11,060 --> 00:17:12,820
Is her own marriage successful?

356
00:17:13,340 --> 00:17:14,580
Don't I know what it's like

357
00:17:14,710 --> 00:17:15,580
when you two argue?

358
00:17:15,888 --> 00:17:17,444
What's that supposed to mean?

359
00:17:18,380 --> 00:17:19,430
How would your sister know

360
00:17:19,430 --> 00:17:20,380
when we argue?

361
00:17:20,430 --> 00:17:22,300
How do I know how she knew?

362
00:17:22,511 --> 00:17:24,333
You don't want this marriage anymore,
do you?

363
00:17:24,377 --> 00:17:25,380
You even told your sister.

364
00:17:25,380 --> 00:17:27,230
Don't over interpret it. Well...

365
00:17:27,230 --> 00:17:28,780
Come on. Let's review it.

366
00:17:29,190 --> 00:17:30,710
Why do we always argue?

367
00:17:32,140 --> 00:17:33,470
Are you kidding me?

368
00:17:33,620 --> 00:17:35,710
Reviewing
when we've been married for years?

369
00:17:36,230 --> 00:17:36,780
This...

370
00:17:38,644 --> 00:17:39,750
How could I have forgotten?

371
00:17:40,060 --> 00:17:42,470
An Ruifeng asked me to go
to the company for a meeting today.

372
00:17:42,470 --> 00:17:43,710
How could I forget?

373
00:17:44,577 --> 00:17:46,140
You only have one day off every week.

374
00:17:46,140 --> 00:17:47,140
Yet you still can't rest?

375
00:17:47,300 --> 00:17:49,430
We're a startup company.

376
00:17:49,430 --> 00:17:50,690
Just wait until we get listed.

377
00:17:50,780 --> 00:17:52,780
Listed? Listed for what?

378
00:17:53,190 --> 00:17:53,670
I'm leaving.

379
00:17:54,100 --> 00:17:55,380
Will you be back for lunch?

380
00:17:55,430 --> 00:17:56,844
I'll order takeout.
Don't bother.

381
00:17:56,844 --> 00:17:58,488
I've already bought the ingredients.

382
00:18:00,190 --> 00:18:00,710
Shen Duole.

383
00:18:00,777 --> 00:18:01,839
Where are you going?

384
00:18:01,840 --> 00:18:03,600
I'm going to the library
with my classmates

385
00:18:03,666 --> 00:18:05,177
to study for excellence.

386
00:18:18,990 --> 00:18:19,540
Yilian.

387
00:18:19,860 --> 00:18:20,750
What are you doing?

388
00:18:21,230 --> 00:18:22,780
I just bought some food.

389
00:18:22,860 --> 00:18:24,711
I'm going back to work
after I finish eating.

390
00:18:24,820 --> 00:18:25,990
Where are you?

391
00:18:26,710 --> 00:18:28,860
I'm about to go to the library.

392
00:18:29,860 --> 00:18:30,510
Look.

393
00:18:30,950 --> 00:18:31,470
Behind me.

394
00:18:32,100 --> 00:18:32,620
Did you see?

395
00:18:33,140 --> 00:18:34,820
There are many lively elderly.

396
00:18:35,710 --> 00:18:37,300
I still think you're the healthiest.

397
00:18:39,511 --> 00:18:40,733
I still have to work hard.

398
00:18:41,044 --> 00:18:42,059
I need to work hard.

399
00:18:42,060 --> 00:18:43,790
Have you taken
your blood pressure medicine?

400
00:18:45,430 --> 00:18:46,470
Not yet.

401
00:18:49,710 --> 00:18:50,710
How worrying.

402
00:18:50,777 --> 00:18:52,755
You have to take
antihypertensive drugs regularly.

403
00:18:52,820 --> 00:18:54,620
Otherwise, it will harm your health.

404
00:18:56,466 --> 00:18:58,270
I've taken my medicine.
I'm just kidding you.

405
00:18:59,030 --> 00:18:59,540
But

406
00:19:00,780 --> 00:19:01,950
I feel like I can't live

407
00:19:02,670 --> 00:19:03,710
without you.

408
00:19:05,540 --> 00:19:06,670
Alright, I'll stop talking.

409
00:19:06,933 --> 00:19:07,950
I have to go back to work.

410
00:19:07,950 --> 00:19:09,840
I'm entering the building now.
The signal is bad.

411
00:19:09,844 --> 00:19:10,955
Let's talk later.

412
00:19:11,620 --> 00:19:12,190
Okay.

413
00:19:12,860 --> 00:19:13,300
Yilian.

414
00:19:13,950 --> 00:19:14,950
Don't work too hard.

415
00:19:16,100 --> 00:19:18,466
I'll be waiting for your call
at anytime and anywhere.

416
00:19:19,540 --> 00:19:19,950
Alright.

417
00:19:32,977 --> 00:19:33,933
Okay, it's lunchtime.

418
00:19:33,955 --> 00:19:34,610
Hello, Ms. Lian.

419
00:19:38,817 --> 00:19:41,530
