423
00:20:04,860 --> 00:20:05,670
Today...

424
00:20:06,430 --> 00:20:07,688
Where did the food come from?

425
00:20:07,910 --> 00:20:08,580
Coming.

426
00:20:09,470 --> 00:20:09,860
All done.

427
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:11,300
Hello.

428
00:20:11,990 --> 00:20:12,950
Ms. Lian.

429
00:20:13,510 --> 00:20:16,140
Professor Shen happens to like
snails stuffed with meat.

430
00:20:16,230 --> 00:20:17,222
I know how to make it.

431
00:20:17,288 --> 00:20:18,140
It smells really good.

432
00:20:18,780 --> 00:20:19,300
Yilian.

433
00:20:19,555 --> 00:20:21,955
I'll ask my children
to call you Aunt Lian from now on.

434
00:20:22,540 --> 00:20:23,270
Sure.

435
00:20:24,030 --> 00:20:25,140
I think it's a good idea.

436
00:20:26,060 --> 00:20:28,380
