437
00:20:29,820 --> 00:20:31,380
No, I think it's pretty good.

438
00:20:31,380 --> 00:20:32,866
Just do whatever Professor Shen says.

439
00:20:33,100 --> 00:20:34,266
Get her a set

440
00:20:34,266 --> 00:20:35,820
- of bowl and chopsticks.
- Okay.

441
00:20:35,820 --> 00:20:37,060
I'll get them myself.

442
00:20:37,060 --> 00:20:37,710
Just sit down.

443
00:20:37,800 --> 00:20:39,470
Just eat the ready-made food today.

444
00:20:39,990 --> 00:20:40,340
Sit down.

445
00:20:40,670 --> 00:20:41,100
Sure.

446
00:20:41,620 --> 00:20:42,950
I'll eat this then.

447
00:20:43,622 --> 00:20:45,266
Don't just eat the rice with toppings.

448
00:20:45,430 --> 00:20:47,030
You can eat whatever you want.

449
00:20:47,060 --> 00:20:47,340
Here.

450
00:20:48,620 --> 00:20:49,750
Try Aunt Lian's cooking.

451
00:20:52,430 --> 00:20:53,270
When eating shrimp,

452
00:20:53,910 --> 00:20:56,380
