the black vein in the middle.

453
00:20:56,977 --> 00:20:58,577
Although it's a bit troublesome,

454
00:20:59,300 --> 00:21:00,140
it doesn't bother me.

455
00:21:00,580 --> 00:21:00,950
Look.

456
00:21:01,600 --> 00:21:03,430
Professor Shen,
you have such skillful hands.

457
00:21:07,580 --> 00:21:07,910
Look.

458
00:21:08,230 --> 00:21:08,860
It's out now.

459
00:21:09,060 --> 00:21:09,780
It's true.

460
00:21:09,780 --> 00:21:10,710
It doesn't bother me.

461
00:21:12,377 --> 00:21:13,270
Why aren't you eating?

462
00:21:14,377 --> 00:21:15,911
Here, dig in. Dip it in vinegar.

463
00:21:17,866 --> 00:21:18,300
Come on.

464
00:21:18,510 --> 00:21:18,780
Dig in.

465
00:21:19,100 --> 00:21:19,430
Dig in.

466
00:21:19,580 --> 00:21:19,950
Okay.

467
00:21:21,670 --> 00:21:23,100
I'm going to eat this snail.

468
00:21:25,820 --> 00:21:26,950
Dad, you guys eat.

469
00:21:27,510 --> 00:21:29,100
I'll go home to put away the clothes.

470
00:21:29,222 --> 00:21:30,060
I'll go back and eat.

471
00:21:30,270 --> 00:21:30,780
Sure.

472
00:21:30,780 --> 00:21:32,100
Let me add more food for you.

473
00:21:32,100 --> 00:21:32,820
Okay, sure.

474
00:21:32,860 --> 00:21:33,380
It's enough.

475
00:21:33,380 --> 00:21:34,400
Let me give you some more.

476
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:35,030
No need.

477
00:21:35,100 --> 00:21:35,688
You guys eat.

478
00:21:37,140 --> 00:21:37,750
Lina.

479
00:21:39,190 --> 00:21:40,060
Recently,

480
00:21:40,444 --> 00:21:41,977
I keep forgetting to take my medicine.

481
00:21:42,910 --> 00:21:45,510
It's dangerous if I don't take
the high blood pressure medicine.

482
00:21:45,910 --> 00:21:48,380
I asked Aunt Lian to supervise me.

483
00:21:50,620 --> 00:21:51,910
Tell Shen Qing

484
00:21:52,540 --> 00:21:54,620
that Aunt Lian will move in next week.

485
00:22:00,780 --> 00:22:01,510
Here.

486
00:22:02,133 --> 00:22:02,540
This one.

487
00:22:02,955 --> 00:22:04,780
Don't work so hard
that you end up not eating.

488
00:22:04,780 --> 00:22:05,340
Okay.

489
00:22:06,950 --> 00:22:07,710
Fragrance.

490
00:22:17,230 --> 00:22:17,710
Shen Qing.

491
00:22:19,540 --> 00:22:20,910
Your stepmother is coming.

492
00:22:21,100 --> 00:22:22,190
Stepmother?

493
00:22:22,190 --> 00:22:23,622
What nonsense are you talking about?

494
00:22:23,860 --> 00:22:25,950
Ms. Lian is moving in.

495
00:22:26,222 --> 00:22:27,270
They're moving in together.

496
00:22:28,733 --> 00:22:31,060
It's going to rain,
and your dad is going to get married.

497
00:22:31,430 --> 00:22:33,100
This isn't
a simple romantic relationship.

498
00:22:33,990 --> 00:22:34,750
Shen Qing.

499
00:22:34,800 --> 00:22:36,888
Your stepmother
is only a few years older than you.

500
00:22:37,190 --> 00:22:37,950
How do you feel?

501
00:22:38,177 --> 00:22:40,100
It's not even settled yet.
Don't talk nonsense.

502
00:22:41,470 --> 00:22:43,510
"High blood pressure is dangerous,"

503
00:22:43,540 --> 00:22:46,190
"so I've asked Aunt Lian
to supervise me."

504
00:22:47,950 --> 00:22:49,820
Am I not a human being?
Can't I supervise him?

505
00:22:50,140 --> 00:22:51,620
I've already set the alarm on my phone

506
00:22:51,620 --> 00:22:52,820
to ring three times a day.

507
00:22:53,230 --> 00:22:54,820
No, they're moving in together?

508
00:22:54,820 --> 00:22:56,780
Isn't it too fast?

509
00:22:57,177 --> 00:22:59,400
Shen Dai doesn't even know
about their relationship yet.

510
00:22:59,430 --> 00:23:00,140
Now great.

511
00:23:00,430 --> 00:23:01,030
She'll explode.

512
00:23:01,300 --> 00:23:02,340
Don't tell Dai.

513
00:23:02,733 --> 00:23:04,190
It's already chaotic enough.

514
00:23:04,200 --> 00:23:05,733
She'll make a scene if she finds out.

515
00:23:05,733 --> 00:23:07,000
Are we not going to say anything?

516
00:23:07,288 --> 00:23:09,000
Are we keeping it a secret forever?

517
00:23:10,670 --> 00:23:11,540
Now,

518
00:23:11,540 --> 00:23:14,230
this new lung cancer-targeted drug,
M701,

519
00:23:14,230 --> 00:23:16,270
has entered
the first phase of clinical trials.

520
00:23:16,580 --> 00:23:18,470
Your company's patented NPI

521
00:23:18,750 --> 00:23:21,580
will greatly advance
the research and development.

522
00:23:21,820 --> 00:23:24,030
Once M701 is successfully launched,

523
00:23:24,430 --> 00:23:26,860
the tumor remission rate
for terminal lung cancer

524
00:23:27,270 --> 00:23:30,380
will reach 62.9%.

525
00:23:31,710 --> 00:23:32,470
It's amazing.

526
00:23:33,820 --> 00:23:35,950
What you have here is truly amazing.

527
00:23:36,910 --> 00:23:39,030
My mother had primary lung cancer.

528
00:23:39,580 --> 00:23:41,750
Five years later,
it metastasized to the breast

529
00:23:41,990 --> 00:23:43,060
chest, and head.

530
00:23:43,377 --> 00:23:44,911
In the end, her illness was beyond cure.

531
00:23:45,300 --> 00:23:47,580
So M701 holds extraordinary significance

532
00:23:47,950 --> 00:23:49,430
for me.

533
00:23:50,950 --> 00:23:52,510
During business negotiation,

534
00:23:52,510 --> 00:23:55,340
we shouldn't
talk about our private affairs,

535
00:23:55,430 --> 00:23:57,060
but why did we bring it up?

536
00:23:57,060 --> 00:23:59,510
It's because we want to express

537
00:24:00,030 --> 00:24:01,990
that this matter is closely related

538
00:24:01,990 --> 00:24:02,990
to all of us.

539
00:24:03,030 --> 00:24:05,510
It's also to express our sincerity
in purchasing.

540
00:24:06,288 --> 00:24:08,510
We also know that any patent's
research and development

541
00:24:08,510 --> 00:24:09,470
is very difficult.

542
00:24:09,820 --> 00:24:11,430
The effort and cost invested

543
00:24:11,580 --> 00:24:13,190
can't be measured in money,

544
00:24:13,270 --> 00:24:13,670
but

545
00:24:14,430 --> 00:24:16,100
given our company's current strength,

546
00:24:16,670 --> 00:24:17,780
the highest price

547
00:24:18,430 --> 00:24:19,380
we can offer

548
00:24:20,030 --> 00:24:22,030
is 6.8 million US dollars.

549
00:24:38,620 --> 00:24:40,060
Mr. An, Mr. Shen.

550
00:24:40,620 --> 00:24:42,710
We will be honored if we can contribute

551
00:24:42,777 --> 00:24:44,377
to the Chinese pharmaceutical industry.

552
00:24:44,620 --> 00:24:45,860
We also recognize

553
00:24:45,950 --> 00:24:47,300
that China is a huge market.

554
00:24:48,670 --> 00:24:49,430
So

555
00:24:50,230 --> 00:24:51,860
we also hope to achieve

556
00:24:51,860 --> 00:24:53,820
a deep and close cooperation
with your company.

557
00:24:54,430 --> 00:24:55,140
We accept

558
00:24:56,140 --> 00:24:56,620
this price.

559
00:24:58,230 --> 00:24:59,100
Great.

560
00:24:59,540 --> 00:25:00,300
Thank you.

561
00:25:00,860 --> 00:25:01,510
Thank you.

